Package: verityx3p
Title: Native X3P (ISO 25178-72) Reader and Writer
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Eric", "Hare", , "ericrhare@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Read and write X3P (ISO 25178-72) 3D surface-topography files via
    the Verity Rust core, so files round-trip bit-identically with the other
    Verity language bindings. Part of the Verity forensic surface-comparison
    project.
